title: About
text:
I am Jack Xu, a thirteen year old who loves birds! My account -> https://www.github.com/jackxu3 Email -> bluebird.jack.xu@gmail.com
My project is about how light pollution affects migratory birds, such as gulls, by reducing rest time and increasing flight speed. Link -> https://github.com/jackxu3/bird-light-pollution

text:
I got the bird migration dataset from Kaggle and the light pollution dataset from Globe at Night.
I cleaned the downloaded data by removing unwanted columns and kept the Latitude, Longitude, and LimitingMag columns.
I removed rows before with no value by piping to na.omit().
